# hilbertMatrix

- _hilbertMatrix(n)_

Answer the _n×n_ Hilbert matrix with elements of the form _1 / (i + j - 1)_.

3×3 Hilbert matrix:

```
>>> 3.hilbertMatrix
[
	1/1 1/2 1/3;
	1/2 1/3 1/4;
	1/3 1/4 1/5
]
```

